ImplementationNotes


Behavior we did not have time to implement:

We implemented all features from our initial SAD.


Future improvements if more time:

If we had more time, we would have added the following features:

 - Separate score display at the end of a 2 player game
 		At the end of each game, display scores of both players in a separate panel with a "Player X wins!" message.


 - Simultaeneous 2p games
 		Have a 2p game mode where both players are on the map simultaenously.


 - Smooth movement
 		Make LivingUnits move smoothly from one grid block to the next, as opposed to instantaneously.


 - Additional enemies
 		More enemy types with different graphics/effects/difficulty.


 - Additional powerups
 		More powerup types with different graphics/effects.